1
00:00:00,113 --> 00:00:02,360
My name is Sobhan Khalil Ahmad

2
00:00:03,433 --> 00:00:05,743
Known as Abu Ahmad al-Sabbagh

3
00:00:06,961 --> 00:00:09,720
We are currently at the <i>Hisba</i> [morality police] base

4
00:00:11,108 --> 00:00:14,147
The <i>Hisba</i> base prison, in the Souq al-Shaarin area

5
00:00:15,368 --> 00:00:19,924
This prison at the <i>Hisba</i> headquarters was where
they brought people who sold packs of cigarettes

6
00:00:20,199 --> 00:00:23,898
And violators concerning beards, and the <i>izar</i> [long pants]

7
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:29,702
They enforced <i>sharia</i> punishments here, they called them <i>sharia</i> punishments

8
00:00:30,406 --> 00:00:34,011
Like flogging, beating, and fines

9
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:36,479
This is the base

10
00:00:37,739 --> 00:00:40,617
They made it a prison and also a storeroom for satellite TV receivers

11
00:00:41,805 --> 00:00:47,383
All these devices belonged to people—they took them and gathered them here

12
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:54,430
They used to issue receipts here, in this room

13
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:58,040
This is the <i>Hisba</i> base

14
00:01:01,905 --> 00:01:02,911
This prison

15
00:01:04,278 --> 00:01:06,932
They used to call this prison the light prison

16
00:01:08,231 --> 00:01:12,980
The light prison, meaning the prisoners in it were the ones they deemed violators

17
00:01:13,817 --> 00:01:19,012
He trims his beard, or wears his <i>izar</i> long, or smokes cigarettes

18
00:01:19,313 --> 00:01:20,993
This was called the light prison
